# Handled Home — Add-on Specs: Provider Onboarding Screen Inventory + Supabase Schema + RLS Checklist
**Adds to:** Provider Onboarding / BYOC PRD Addendum  
**Goal:** Give Lovable an unambiguous build target: routes, components, tables, policies, indexes, and minimal APIs.

---

# PART A — Screen Inventory (Routes + Components)

> Naming is illustrative. Match your current routing conventions.

## A1) Provider Entry & Opportunity
### `/(auth)/role-select`
**Purpose:** Choose customer vs provider  
**Components:**
- RoleChoiceCard (Customer / Provider)
- ContinueButton

### `/provider/entry/categories`
**Purpose:** Select categories (multi-select)  
**Components:**
- CategoryMultiSelect (chips)
- ContinueButton

### `/provider/entry/coverage`
**Purpose:** Home base + service area (ZIPs or zones)  
**Components:**
- InputHomeBaseZip
- MultiZipPicker OR ZonePicker
- ContinueButton

### `/provider/opportunity`
**Purpose:** Show dynamic “Good News” banner based on zone×category state  
**Components:**
- OpportunityBanner (variant A–E)
- OpportunityBenefitsList
- FoundingPartnerBadge (optional)
- CTAButton (Apply Now / Join Waitlist)
**Logic:**
- Resolve ZIPs → zone_id(s)
- For each selected category, fetch `market_zone_category_state`
- Compute best banner variant (priority: EARLY > OPEN > WAITLIST > CLOSED)

