# PART D — Indexes & Constraints (Performance + Integrity)

## D1) Unique constraints
- `provider_org_coverage` unique (org_id, zone_id, category_key)
- `provider_agreement_acceptance` unique (application_id, clause_key)
- `byoc_invite_links` token unique

## D2) Indexes
- `provider_applications(status, created_at)`
- `provider_org_coverage(zone_id, category_key, status)`
- `provider_agreement_acceptance(application_id)`
- `provider_compliance_documents(org_id, status)`
- `byoc_invite_events(invite_id, created_at)`
- `byoc_activations(provider_org_id, activated_at)`

