# PART E — Minimal API / RPC Contracts (Lovable-friendly)

## E1) Resolve opportunity banner
**RPC:** `get_provider_opportunity(user_zip_list, category_list)`  
Returns:
- zone_id(s)
- per-category market state
- best banner variant
- founding partner slots remaining (if tracked)

## E2) Create/Resume application
**RPC:** `get_or_create_provider_application(user_id)`  
Returns application id + saved progress.

## E3) Submit application
**RPC:** `submit_provider_application(application_id)`  
Validates:
- required fields complete
- all agreement clauses accepted
- payout setup status (if required)
Then sets status SUBMITTED/UNDER_REVIEW.

## E4) Create BYOC invite link
**RPC:** `create_byoc_invite_link(org_id, zone_id, category_key, sku_id, default_level_id, cadence, credit_preset_id?)`

## E5) BYOC activation (token gate)
**Edge Function:** `activate_byoc_invite(token, customer_user_id, property_id, payment_method_id)`  
Validates token, creates activation, links provider, sets up service/routine item.

