# PART F — Acceptance Tests (Must Pass)

## F1) Provider onboarding
- Provider sees correct opportunity banner based on zone/category state.
- Provider can complete wizard, accept all clauses, connect payouts, and submit.
- Draft persists across app close/reopen.
- Ops can approve and provider sees approved state.

## F2) Agreement acceptance
- Each clause requires a tap.
- Cannot submit until all required clauses accepted.
- Acceptance log visible to ops.

## F3) BYOC
- Approved provider can generate invite link and share scripts.
- Customer can activate via token and attach payment.
- Activation creates mapped service (SKU + Level) without manual ops steps.
